{"hcf0c37c2geb57g44f7gb1bbgdfef07d51de8": ["Hmm. As far as solutions go, poison is so... final.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "a6a5dd71-c905-9d1c-b005-9fd015034751"], "hffa0edcag71f5g4d25gaf7cg8c3b4eb1406c": ["Poison, eh? Not sure I could do it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "a6a5dd71-c905-9d1c-b005-9fd015034751"], "he2ba1764g82a9g4066ga6adg50dddeefc302": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "a6a5dd71-c905-9d1c-b005-9fd015034751"], "ha550062cg1eb2g4f3bga5e3g271955d0e383": ["Poison? It's certainly a direct approach.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "a6a5dd71-c905-9d1c-b005-9fd015034751"], "he2fb31c6ga35fg4463gb1e3g402c9c5c8388": ["  | I want to know your opinion on X. (Shadowheart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "a6a5dd71-c905-9d1c-b005-9fd015034751"], "ha5deff20gf767g4d42ga9eagdee0cbd6577d": ["Taking our lives is certainly one solution to our problem.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "a6a5dd71-c905-9d1c-b005-9fd015034751"], "hb0d7b3c4g141ag42b1gbb88g2028c11b57f3": ["  | I want to know your opinion on X. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "a6a5dd71-c905-9d1c-b005-9fd015034751"], "h4f9713c1g5f49g42cbgbbf9gbfcfa5800d34": ["Poison. I suppose that's one way to fix a monster eating you from the inside out.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "a6a5dd71-c905-9d1c-b005-9fd015034751"], "h015afd34g76f1g4ff8g9269g799e8b09bc7c": ["Hold on to it. Better dead than one of... <i>them.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "h9b15e8ceg5ca9g42e4g875ag1d42b71b8e2a": ["Keep it. And be ready to use it, if you must.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "had64c3ffgdb4dg402egadf0g976c945936f0": ["| I want option A (Asterion Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "h9a059c95gf1a1g4f17ga245ge40830d822a3": ["| I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "hee423313gc396g4ee9gbc50ge22c9c2457c6": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "hf4976ee3g07fag427eg9e03g121af47217a2": ["Might be happy to have it, if the only other option is <i>tentacles.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "h3cf29437gf9e9g4dbfg9f8dg7b74c8a2672b": ["| I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "h01c64a04g5d16g4d45g940bg7bd6838678be": ["| I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "h4d808aa7g37bfg4390g90acgf5be7009df5b": ["We should keep the poison. Just in case.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4fc8136e-f342-91cb-2316-2e4c244f5a9d"], "h0af75da6g401ag4d84g8b7dgbe2f6ae4a378": ["Yes - hold on to it. Better dead than one of... <i>them.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "ha35796b5ge0feg4dccg8070g2b82be7eccd1": ["Keep it, agreed. And be ready to use it, if we must.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "he231fcddgb4fcg4bf2g84c0gaba036c84664": ["Exactly. It'll be so much cleaner if you start to turn.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "h2080437agf1dfg409fg842bg9cfc69dcc1d4": ["| I agree. I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "h4edc5d0bge640g40c4gb79ege91ec5e5c525": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "hc6a43390gc547g4959g8ab7g8897cc5b2e67": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "h116fc5e4g7e3fg422cg8fe7gf432b9799945": ["| I agree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "h45811938g1be2g4ee4ga751g4bcf755398e6": ["| I agree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "h9957fa9eg9fe9g4a87ga93fge67ba51cb291": ["Better to keep it on hand. I'd rather die fast, if I have the choice.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "c8bffadc-620d-f1d4-244d-fa1a47d37fec"], "hc276edbdg67afg4c17g8692g2261df62cd72": ["Yes - hold on to it. Better dead than one of... <i>them.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "h1056306egea02g47ecgbc0bg1d389d1505d5": ["Keep it, agreed. And be ready to use it, if we must.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "h1cc5f9b7gd4fcg429bgb81fg9c7d3c3bd6a8": ["Exactly. It'll be so much cleaner if you start to turn.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "h22001077geeb7g4337gbb5bga1e346bb3c98": ["| I agree. I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "h8427bc23ge175g46acgab5dgb7dcb669f8bd": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "h06079afbg886eg4678g8207g71d3478042fa": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "h969af32bg6524g4ebag985ag32832546e5fc": ["| I agree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "h7dec9609gac34g40e8g9f55g7cf47814beee": ["| I agree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "hed5ec80fg4253g4ac7gb351gc02055038550": ["Never look a poisonous horse in the mouth. Well... keep it, anyway.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "2c4702ef-1266-f8fc-2ba3-8353f0acbdbe"], "h58b5f61eg71a3g4f05ga1e2gccd6ced31bae": ["Yes - hold on to it. Better dead than one of... <i>them.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "hbda1fdb4g98dfg4b64gab45g76d61ba96b8a": ["Keep it, agreed. And be ready to use it, if we must.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "h7dabf6f2gf340g47c4g9b1egd26e1f96d77c": ["Exactly. It'll be so much cleaner if you start to turn.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "h76b0e18fgb2feg4e10g9ef5gf1f3f8c3425e": ["| I agree. I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "h78c6451cg8c0eg451bgb296g20a7b8677ca5": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "hdee182bbgf557g4340gab9bgd6dd0978ecc3": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "h2d0d07e1g6b11g4fc7ga42ege542acd4061c": ["| I agree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "h4eb1f489g993ag44a6g8e0fg81c0d5520bb1": ["| I agree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "h3acf243dg3611g48ccg90e9g7c581b42fe4f": ["It's best to have an escape plan. Even if the escape is... permanent.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "ed2ef32a-4e5d-ca26-19a9-baffc71cf5b1"], "h2fc03d01gea45g4e0bga154g14c945dc7cee": ["Let's talk about something more pleasant next time. Puppies, maybe. Or whiskey.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "heee8fdb0g75eag462bgb0fdgc4cfa0b15914": ["Do as you wish, should the time come. Far be it from me to stop you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "haf17dd72ge73fg4329g814cg0e370a2f1ad5": ["Let's go. At this rate I'll die of boredom before the poison gets me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "h57415d30g1c00g4b81gb99fg5c0edb5cd915": ["| Well we don't need to decide right now. (Shadowheart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "hb10263a6ge91ag4d26gb29agaea69936a1d0": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "h556d2b61gf50dg49b3g8bbbg122d5af12a23": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "hf01960eeg42dbg4964gb7aeg70206ce07dca": ["| Well we don't need to decide right now. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "h7d8bac14geee8g407bg9b54gc011488fbe5c": ["| Well we don't need to decide right now. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "h64733311g0b84g4a38g9e7bg4937e260bae5": ["Clearly we're not going to agree on this. Better to keep moving.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "8e9cddee-84d9-babd-48a8-d9e6b694eb21"], "h4f82351eg3721g477dg9855g5ee6e6114de5": ["A death pact? Things keep going from worse to ever worser.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "hd3d7340fg51e3g4d85g8d3bgd64e59e06e89": ["We have our contingency, should the worst come to pass.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "h8e57af76g1615g4740gbae6g01a9483f4caf": ["Excellent. Although when it comes to passing that vial around, I won't be taking the first sip.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "hecaa9388g899fg4e9cgbdbdg30ffcf83040a": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Shadowheart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "h71e3535egdd83g4059g89adgbda772df9b49": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "hf16c6a66g5e56g419dg950ag827b087c686b": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "hec1acee7g795fg4501g9bf5gc60bba946d03": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "hc2a6c388gdb93g4dc2g9c8cg3d240101664a": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "h37eb1b72ga4d1g411fg8281g9899432d8743": ["The poison's staying with us, then. For the best.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "473475a5-1641-2bef-ec38-3898832f8195"], "h8df8455bg46f3g4c3bga107g5262e9cabf79": ["Nice. Confidence looks good on me!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "5d1c6940-3d87-de18-2956-55091db99003"], "hb070c615g0c2eg4b13g9723g77a262ecb55a": ["We are agreed - let us speak of the poison no more.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "5d1c6940-3d87-de18-2956-55091db99003"], "h54ff2dd1g918cg42edgaeafgfc91242c4d9c"