if you must.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "fa10c708-24c5-1700-95b2-0cf782fa432e"], "h781461e7gbc66g4c38ga926g3c4866a57e64": ["Do keep it. I don't want to get my hands dirty if you start to turn.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "fa10c708-24c5-1700-95b2-0cf782fa432e"], "hae609c08g2bf3g4291gbfdbg20a663928678": ["| I disagree. I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "fa10c708-24c5-1700-95b2-0cf782fa432e"], "h57b8cb8cg4efcg4f7fga05eg5d7a0760f54f": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "fa10c708-24c5-1700-95b2-0cf782fa432e"], "h11060cf2g7f23g44b2ga9b5g00c987ef825f": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "fa10c708-24c5-1700-95b2-0cf782fa432e"], "hcd632d30ga398g4693gb239gceda70caf232": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "fa10c708-24c5-1700-95b2-0cf782fa432e"], "h28438b7dgaf9eg4b55gaf4cgdf7bb613c7e3": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "fa10c708-24c5-1700-95b2-0cf782fa432e"], "h0afa9036g9222g4e2bgbef3g23a8af65305a": ["Unless you have a cure right now, we need to keep that poison.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "fa10c708-24c5-1700-95b2-0cf782fa432e"], "hbafe0d82g3110g44edgade3g03719966c3f5": ["Forget the poison, for sure. I vanquished a griffon - I can vanquish this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "h4d3be569g1fcag4d52g8cebg0237c594ac50": ["Poison? Never. I shall sllit my own throat if it comes to that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "h027d70bfg5a75g4055gb3c4g96f88d33fc56": ["Exactly, let's drop it down the first well we find.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "hf2bee987g6408g4736ga35cg70551f994d09": ["| I agree. I want option B (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "h675d4736ga968g4d05ga1a1g08ba63612b4d": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "hc83da312g1407g4da4g9599g5dad0050de5a": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "h0f6dd76fgb552g4af9g8424gf0190180b678": ["| I agree. I want option B (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "he2e6610ag40d7g4379g9275gc5c1114e2a31": ["| I agree. I want option B (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "h4316cf9fg84e3g47d6g9833gf2017ccab05f": ["Less weight in the pack is always better, so that's my vote.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "4e0fbb18-9243-ac85-d8dc-d9aa870a3449"], "h76505ec6g04fbg4bb4gba5ag5c9534ecf2b8": ["Forget the poison. I vanquished a griffon - I can vanquish this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "cc8ad9a4-070d-2754-a9a0-683b8c1b6e58"], "hafb6e2c4g95c5g4126ga3b1gf1363b355240": ["Poison? Never. I shall sllit my own throat if it comes to that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "cc8ad9a4-070d-2754-a9a0-683b8c1b6e58"], "h1e80f4e6g234ag4c63g8d8bgeb0de24dd4e1": ["Nonsense. Let's drop it down the first well we find.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "cc8ad9a4-070d-2754-a9a0-683b8c1b6e58"], "he1c7d677gbf3bg4281gb928ga7cc02e56e53": ["| I disagree. I want option B (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "cc8ad9a4-070d-2754-a9a0-683b8c1b6e58"], "h978878f8gb3c6g4f3fgb449g1b21c5601677": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "cc8ad9a4-070d-2754-a9a0-683b8c1b6e58"], "h42ab313egb982g4f22g83a6g06a7654d07e6": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "cc8ad9a4-070d-2754-a9a0-683b8c1b6e58"], "h975a72ccg4289g4eaega753g3a36cf3c6d90": ["| I disagree. I want option B (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide.html", "cc8ad9a4-070d-2754-a9a0-683b8c1b6e58"], "he0960cb8g5ce0g4ee4g9ca3gd93e55518a0a": ["| I disagree. I want option B (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Compa